#!/usr/bin/env python3
"""
kalshi-pm-analyzer — Full pipeline runner for Kalshi/Polymarket analysis.

USAGE:
    ./kalshi-pm-analyzer <mode> [--model MODEL]
    ./kalshi-pm-analyzer finalize
    ./kalshi-pm-analyzer backtest

MODES:
    incremental | full | deep | anomaly
    pm-incremental | pm-full | pm-deep | pm-anomaly

WHAT THIS SCRIPT DOES:
    Step 1 (automated): Runs the scan and writes raw candidates to batch files
                        so research subagents have their input ready.
    Steps 2-5 (agent):  Prints explicit instructions for the LLM agent to execute
                        in order — research, classify, verify, finalize.

No hermes_tools or any agent-runtime dependency required. Any LLM agent can follow
the printed instructions using web search, file read/write, and terminal tools.
"""

